      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/6825396-la-isla-bajo-el-mar">Quotes from Island Beneath th...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;We all have an unsuspected reserve of strength inside that emerges when life puts us to the test.&rdquo;</span>
